kw.name: Start Process
kw.doc: Starts a new process on background.

kw.name: Sleep
kw.doc: Pauses the test executed for the given time.

kw.name: Get Environment Variable
kw.doc: Returns the value of an environment variable with the given name.

kw.name: Open Browser
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to given URL.

kw.name: Go To
kw.doc: Navigates the active browser instance to the provided URL.

kw.name: Wait Until Page Contains
kw.doc: Waits until `text` appears on current page.

kw.name: Execute Javascript
kw.doc: Executes the given JavaScript code.

kw.name: Set Variable
kw.doc: Returns the given values which can then be assigned to a variables.

kw.name: Run Keyword If
kw.doc: Runs the given keyword with the given arguments, if ``condition`` is true.

kw.name: Capture Page Screenshot
kw.doc: Takes a screenshot of the current page and embeds it into the log.

kw.name: Run Keyword If
kw.doc: Runs the given keyword with the given arguments, if ``condition`` is true.

kw.name: Fail
kw.doc: Fails the test with the given message and optionally alters its tags.

kw.name: Terminate Process
kw.doc: Stops the process gracefully or forcefully.

kw.name: Close Browser
kw.doc: Closes the current browser.
